				<outline text="&lt;span&gt;Why isn't this accessible through the API, so we can flow formatting and links through to Facebook posts from our blogging tools?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;" created="Tue, 06 Sep 2016 18:06:52 GMT" />
