				<outline text="If all goes well, it will be updated once every day at 12PM Eastern (midnight) with a single item, the stories from my &lt;a href=&quot;http://radio3.io/users/davewiner/&quot;&gt;linkblog&lt;/a&gt; from the previous day.&amp;nbsp;" created="Thu, 08 Sep 2016 12:49:37 GMT" />
